    "data": [
        {
            "title": "中國2025年財政支出未達目標 在穩成長與遏制地方債務風險之間求平衡",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg calculations based on data from China's Ministry of Finance\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"584\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/YcyWmrmhlx766u2rdQIeuw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4NA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/55eaca2a54d3b3d689c99a205ff596e4\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg calculations based on data from China's Ministry of Finance</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 2025年中國政府支出連續第七年低於預算計畫，在經濟承壓時為政策提供了更大的騰挪空間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博基於財政部周五公佈數據計算得出，去年政府在兩個主要預算一般公共預算和政府性基金預算下的總支出為40萬億元人民幣（5.8萬億美元）。該數值較去年初計畫數值低約5%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此舉凸顯出北京方面正努力在支持經濟與遏制地方借貸風險之間尋求平衡。中國上次超額支出發生在2018年，當時正值唐納德·川普首個總統任期中美爆發貿易戰期間。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-28be1865-7250-328a-93dd-8e2c77341e4b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"584\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nNKNiCgZ7R7ScIXGUeO0yg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4NA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/888f20bebbf8ca8826ca7bbbe161127a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">支出較上年成長近4%，較政府總收入高出12.7萬億元人民幣，赤字創下紀錄新高。然而，支出成長並未完全用於支撐經濟成長，因為其中很大一部分資金被用於為地方政府的表外債務進行再融資。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鑒於未來數月出口有望保持韌性，政府今年或僅會小幅增加支出，一方面面臨財政增收壓力，另一方面仍需持續推進地方債務風險化解工作。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">去年上半年，隨著政府為應對川普關稅政策對出口的衝擊而緊急提振內需，總支出成長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但隨著對其他市場的強勁出口完全抵消了對美出口下滑的影響，下半年支出放緩 —— 導致投資和消費降溫。10月與川普政府達成的關稅休戰協議進一步降低了中國官員的緊迫感。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此外，彭博匯編數據顯示，通過新增地方政府專項債發行籌集的約3.4萬億元人民幣被用於償還所謂的隱性債務。這一規模遠高於預算安排，擠壓了可用於投資的資金空間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">政府還正將投資重心從實物轉向人力資本，押注技術創新和居民收入提升將驅動未來經濟成長並提振消費。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Undershoots 2025 Spending Goal in Sign of Caution on Debt</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Nectar Gan、Yujing Liu、Jing Zhao.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B2025%E5%B9%B4%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E6%94%AF%E5%87%BA%E6%9C%AA%E9%81%94%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99-%E5%9C%A8%E7%A9%A9%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7%E8%88%87%E9%81%8F%E5%88%B6%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E5%82%B5%E5%8B%99%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E4%B9%8B%E9%96%93%E6%B1%82%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1-113000764.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-30 20:18:26",
