        {
            "title": "金銀價格重挫 聯儲會主席提名人選消息提振美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"592\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NtSEO3Ln9.9eP4VFf5MNRw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/9d9dabed1bf990ded9e95eeebf6b9ff2\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 黃金和白銀周五遭大幅拋售，之前創紀錄的漲勢降溫。有報導稱川普政府準備提名凱文·沃什擔任<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲會\">聯儲會</a>主席，這一消息提振了美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">現貨金價重挫逾7%，跌破每盎司5,000美元，延續打破此前創紀錄漲勢的劇烈波動格局。現貨白銀則跌破每盎司100美元。彭博美元即期指數一度漲0.5%，使得貴金屬對多數買家而言變得更貴。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博新聞報導，川普預計將提名沃什為新一任聯儲會主席。這位前聯儲會理事素以通膨鷹派著稱，但近幾個月卻轉向川普的立場，公開支持降息。川普稱，他將於美國時間周五上午宣布聯儲會主席提名人選。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c7ed7e46-cb56-31aa-add0-0e4978a8dbc0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">華僑銀行策略師Christopher Wong表示，金價走勢「印證了漲得快跌得快的警示寓言」。他指出，沃什的提名消息是一個導火索，但回調早已勢在必行。「這就像是市場一直在等待的回調借口，以結束之前的拋物線式上漲。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今年以來，金銀價格已大幅上漲，一些技術指標亮起紅燈。相對強弱指數(RSI)是其中之一，該指標近幾周發出了金銀可能均已超買、即將回調的信號。黃金RSI指標最近觸及90，創數十年來最高水平。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"592\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Cl8Z4qy.ASybTuEylwcqHg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/39817ed1e849cbd28c5bd18b09f9f624\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">即便出現回調，金價1月仍累計上漲約15%。白銀漲幅更是驚人，年初至今上漲逾30%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Gold, Silver Plunge as Reports on Fed Nominee Boost Dollar</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">(新增第二段以下內容)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%87%91%E9%8A%80%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E9%87%8D%E6%8C%AB-%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E6%8F%90%E5%90%8D%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%B8%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E6%8F%90%E6%8C%AF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-095135603.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-30 18:23:22",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "凱雷：金屬剛進入大宗商品超級周期 近期狂熱只是「喜馬拉雅的山腳」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 凱雷集團的Jeff Currie表示，金屬市場正在進入新一輪大宗商品超級周期，近期的狂熱不過是「喜馬拉雅的山腳」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Currie在接受彭博Odd Lots播客的Tracy Alloway和Joe Weisenthal採訪時說：「我們離真正的山峰還差得遠。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他表示，美元主導地位的減弱正推動資金轉向大宗商品。隨著地緣政治風險上升、供應鏈出現裂痕，各國與消費者正轉向黃金、白銀以及銅等關鍵礦產這類「不易被扣押的資產」，從而推升需求並鼓勵囤貨，尤其是白銀。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f3b92484-3c7e-3f71-8006-46fec4f4fe2a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">例如，白銀對中國經濟至關重要：一方面它是太陽能電池板等可再生能源技術的關鍵投入品，而這些技術是中國產業戰略的核心；另一方面，它又是居民可負擔的價值儲藏工具。因此，確保對白銀的獲取在戰略層面與社會層面都很重要。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Currie認為，即便各國政府大力推進放寬許可審批、精簡行政手續，供應也難以迅速跟上，因為大宗商品的生產通常周期長且資本密集。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「所以我才說，現在只是冰山一角……至少會再持續十年。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Carlyle’s Currie Says Commodities Supercycle is Just Beginning</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%87%B1%E9%9B%B7-%E9%87%91%E5%B1%AC%E5%89%9B%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%97%E5%95%86%E5%93%81%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%9F-%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E7%8B%82%E7%86%B1%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF-%E5%96%9C%E9%A6%AC%E6%8B%89%E9%9B%85%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%B1%E8%85%B3-093958510.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-30 18:23:24",
